articles.author: Jack Cozens
articles.title: Off-sequence Ferrari beats Toyota to Le Mans victory again - The Race
articles.description: Ferrari denied Toyota victory in the Le Mans 24 Hours for a second year in a row as Nicklas Nielsen executed an unlikely final stint to win the World Endurance Championship centrepiece by less than 15 seconds.
